      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/clayfield-4011.png" alt="Clayfield 4011 property purchased by Edwards & Smith" />
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/recent-purchases">Recent Purchases</a> / <a href="/brisbane/recent-purchases">Brisbane</a> / <span>Clayfield</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Clayfield, 4011 - Brisbane</h1>
        <p class="property-subtitle">Secured for a professional athlete navigating a busy schedule</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Property Overview -->
    <section class="property-overview section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="overview-grid">
          <div class="overview-main">
            <h2>The Success Story</h2>
            <p class="lead-text">
              House hunting can be challenging when you're a pro athlete constantly on the move, but that's where we come in. Our client needed expert representation to navigate Brisbane's competitive property market while managing the demands of their professional sporting career.
            </p>

            <h3>What We Did</h3>
            <ul class="success-points">
              <li>Conducted targeted property search in Brisbane's premium inner-city suburbs</li>
              <li>Managed all property inspections and due diligence on behalf of our time-poor client</li>
              <li>Identified this exceptional Clayfield property matching their specific criteria</li>
              <li>Provided comprehensive market analysis and property evaluation</li>
              <li>Negotiated purchase and coordinated entire settlement process</li>
              <li>Delivered white-glove service suited to professional athlete's schedule</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Why Clayfield?</h3>
            <p>
              Clayfield represents Brisbane's blue-chip real estate. Our client chose this suburb for its proximity to sporting facilities, excellent transport connections to the CBD and airport, prestigious schools, and the quintessential Brisbane character home appeal. It's a suburb where lifestyle, convenience, and capital growth potential align perfectly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="overview-sidebar">
            <div class="property-card">
              <h3>Property Details</h3>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Location:</span>
                <span class="value">Clayfield, QLD 4011</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Region:</span>
                <span class="value">Brisbane Inner North</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Service Type:</span>
                <span class="value">Full Buyers Agent Service</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Client Type:</span>
                <span class="value">Professional Athlete</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-card">
              <h4>Time-Poor Professional?</h4>
              <p>We specialize in helping busy professionals and athletes secure premium properties without the stress.</p>
              <a href="/book-free-consultation" class="button-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Suburb Insights -->
    <section class="suburb-insights section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Clayfield Suburb Insights</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Why Clayfield is one of Brisbane's most prestigious and sought-after inner-city suburbs.</p>

        <div class="insights-grid">
          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Location & Accessibility</h3>
            <p>Just 6km from Brisbane CBD with excellent public transport. Direct train line to the city. Close to airport for frequent travelers. Perfect for professionals and athletes needing convenient access.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">10/10</div>
            <h3>Schools & Education</h3>
            <p>Home to some of Brisbane's finest schools including Clayfield College and close to Anglican Church Grammar School (Churchie). Top-tier education options make this suburb highly sought-after by families.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Character & Architecture</h3>
            <p>Famous for stunning Queenslander homes and character properties. Tree-lined streets with heritage architecture. The suburb has maintained its classic Brisbane charm while offering modern amenities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Investment & Growth</h3>
            <p>Blue-chip suburb with consistent capital growth. Limited land supply and high demand from affluent buyers. Strong rental yields for quality properties. One of Brisbane's most resilient property markets.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">7/10</div>
            <h3>Parks & Recreation</h3>
            <p>Kedron Brook Bikeway perfect for cycling and walking. Multiple parks and sporting facilities. Close to Eagle Farm Racecourse and premium sporting clubs. Great for active lifestyles.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Lifestyle & Dining</h3>
            <p>Racecourse Road precinct offers excellent caf√©s, restaurants, and boutique shopping. Village atmosphere with upscale amenities. Close to Portside Wharf and Eat Street Markets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

