            <h3>How can Edwards & Smith help me buy in Clayfield?</h3>
            <p>We provide complete buyers agent service including off-market access, property search, inspections, due diligence, negotiation, and settlement. Perfect for time-poor professionals who need expert representation without the stress.</p>
          </div>

